// Semantic direction:
// spill_stdlib is the complete Norscode game engine standard library.
// spill_bygger provides a fluent builder API for configuring and launching a game.
// bygg_kjør enters the game loop, calling app_init → spillsløyfe → app_avslutt.
// standard_komponenter are the built-in ECS components shipped with the engine.
// transform_komp stores lokal and global transform; all renderable nodes need it.
// skript_komp attaches a Norscode function as a per-entity update callback.
// levetid_komp automatically deletes an entity after a specified duration.
// innebygde_systemer are pre-registered systems that run in the standard planlegger.
// transform_system propagates parent transforms down the scene hierarchy.
// sprite_render_system collects sprite_komp entities and submits them to sprite_batch.
// animasjon_system advances anim_2d for all entities with animasjon components.
// fysikk_system runs the fysikk_verden update and syncs rigidbody positions to transforms.
// kollisjon_system detects collisions and fires trigger callbacks.
// spill_kontekst is an ambient context struct passed to all systems and callbacks.
// sk_ressurser gives systems access to the asset bank without global state.
// sk_hendelser is the shared hendelse_ecs bus for all engine and game events.
// nc spill ny prosjekt_navn creates a new game project with the standard layout.
// export_web compiles the game to WASM and packages it with an HTML shell.
// export_mobil targets iOS and Android via cross-compilation.
// spill_test allows headless game simulation for automated testing.
// spill_test_inndata injects synthetic input events into the game loop.
// spill_test_snapshot captures entity state for regression testing.

// Primitive flow:
// nc spill ny Romspill: scaffold project with worlds/, scenes/, assets/, src/
// spill_bygg_ny().tittel("Romspill").fps(60).vsync(true).kjør(spill_app):
//   init ecs verden → registrer standard_komponenter → registrer innebygde_systemer
//   spillsløyfe → oppdater (fysikk → kollisjon → skript) → tegn (sprites + 3D)
// nc spill bygg --eksport web → WASM + HTML → dist/web/
// spill_test: spill_test_frame(10) → assert entitet har stilling {x > 0}

// This defines the game engine stdlib: component/system registry, game builder,
// ambient context, nc spill commands for scaffolding and export, and headless testing.

